verbose_text: The activation of Rac induces the formation of lamellipodia and filopodia at the leading edge, and the reorganization of the actin cytoskeleton, which in turn promotes the accumulation of PDGF receptor, integrin alphavbeta3, and Necl-5 at the leading edge.
